{"tid":296378,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"支足U20踢德國丁組　每隊可獲13萬元仍擬罷踢　籲「勿將聯賽變馬戲團」","createTime":"2017-06-24T13:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T04:01:37.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2faf2085d6993039a95ffb757b02155ace00a4e8","tid":296378,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:48:41.000Z","msg":"為備戰2020年東京奧運，中國足協已和德國足協達成共識，國足U20代表隊下季將參戰德國第4級別的西南地區聯賽。雖然每隊對手將獲1.5萬歐元（13萬港元），但有該聯賽的參賽球隊就大表反對，直指把聯賽變成「馬戲團」。<br />\n<br />\n按中、德兩國足協的協議，下季德國西南地區聯賽將有19支當地球隊及國足U20，雖然後者成績將不計算聯賽積分，而且中國足協會向其他球隊各支付1.5萬歐元，但仍有球隊大力抨擊此計劃。奧伯豪森（Oberhausen）主席Hajo Sommers表示：「這把聯賽變成馬戲團，這樣拜仁慕尼黑就可向中國賣更多球衣吧。」<br />\n<br />\n紅白埃森（Rot-Wiess Essen）主席Michael Welling亦稱：「在這個聯賽，絕對有比協助中國青年球員更重要的事。」至於曼海娒（SV Waldhof Mannheim）則在facebook發表聲明，指球會已有共識拒絕與國足U20對賽，寧可另外進行兩場友賽。"},{"pid":"a503833297e48c66333e465c7093997fb53dc931","tid":296378,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:49:43.000Z","msg":"希望到時真係做到"},{"pid":"6c29859efe976b74f041e8d1f5095719a876a34e","tid":296378,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0301905c0a32459acebca3ad7b11943144a58cea","tid":296378,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:00:00.000Z","msg":"要係咁搭飛機？"},{"pid":"623f85e793b67abf82dd3b5faec333bc8986916b","tid":296378,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bef5fed4f256104cd72789aad30e451d7a83dcf","tid":296378,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af51aa8ac137d2867ae8b3405407f0dfc4749fd","tid":296378,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:15